<h4><a name="cat4-q1"></a>What is Kiindly?</h4>
<p>Kiindly is a company which powers social fundraising for organizations ranging from charities to universities to local groups, all based on Kiindly's proprietary social matching process (aka our secret sauce). Because every penny counts, we help donors participate with organizations and be empowered at the same time. </p>

<h4><a name="cat4-q2"></a>How can I start a Kiindly campaign?</h4>
<p>If you are a charity, non-profit, university, political organization, religious group, local organization, or any other organization looking to fundraise, Kiindly was set up to help you. Please contact us here in order to set up your own campaign.</p>

<h4><a name="cat4-q3"></a>Why should an organization use Kiindly?</h4>
<p>If you want to raise money by empowering your donors versus guilting them, a Kiindly fundraiser is for you.I If you want to raise money leveraging the power of social media and the insights of behavioral science, then a Kiindly fundraiser is for you. We believe that the essence of fundraising is about the donor and the donor relationship. Through years of work in behavioral science and online technology, Kiindly discovered that donors want exactly what fundraising organizations want: for every penny to count. As a result, the Kiindly Penny Pledge and our other social matching products, which are proprietary to Kiindly, work better and quicker than other fundraisers because every penny does count.</p>

<h4><a name="cat4-q4"></a>Are there any start up costs for a Kiindly campaign?</h4>
<p>There are no start up costs for a typical Kiindly campaign. Kiindly does offer custom consulting services for organizations that desire greater assistance. Kiindly will provide custom consulting to help such organizations to develop the specific creative and messaging for an organization's campaign. These services are provided on a fee basis.</p>
